parameters:
Stripping naked, she thrusts the back of her head into the
public toilet bowl. Despite having agreed to this, the
humiliation is unbelievable. Her silky hair soaks up the
toilet water, sending shivers of indescribable discomfort
through her body.

Thug: To think that the great Shark Duchess is now being
treated like a toilet... You never know what's gonna happen,
huh? What a sight... heh heh heh...

Thug: Hey, open your mouth! I'm gonna give you plenty to
drink... I'll mark your insides with my piss!

Memimi: (N-noooo... I really hate this!! It's filthy...
lying naked on the toilet floor, head dunked in the bowl...!
This is already unimaginably unclean...!!)

Even for the city's strongest monster, Shark Duchess, as a
teenage girl with common sense, being in such unsanitary
conditions is unbearable. And to be forced to drink waste...
it's absolutely detestable.

Should she scream and run away? Should she cry and beg for
mercy? There might be many options to avoid drinking
urine... but pride is a shackle that constantly binds
Memimi...
Memimi: A-ah... hurry up and pour it...

Thug: You've got some guts, Shark Duchess-sama! No holding
back... here I go!!

Memimi: !!!? Bwaaahhhhh... buahhh!!! It stinks... remember
this!?

Memimi: (He really did it... he really pissed in my
mouth...!! Uwaaaahhh... it's dirty! It smells fishy... it's
kinda salty and warm and it feels disgusting!!)

A yellow arc streams into her widely opened mouth... hitting
her tongue and teeth, splashing about and dirtying Memimi's
face. A puddle of urine forms inside her small mouth... and
gets sucked down her throat...

Memimi: Gulp... bleh, gulp...! It's so stinky... ughhh...!!
I'm drinking it... ugh, bleh...!

Memimi: (Eek, this is the worst... I have no choice but to
drink it...! Waste is filling my mouth...! It's being
absorbed into my stomach...!)

Thug: Heheheh, she's really drinking it... The sense of
conquest is unreal!! Aren't you gonna let it out?

Thug: W-wait a sec... I can't go well when someone's next to
me... Oh, here it comes, here it comes...!
Memimi: Gulp, blub... eh!? Wha-... how do I- stop...!

Memimi: Bwaaaghhhhhhhhhhhh!!!? Blargh, gurgle, gargle!!!
Cough, gag, blargh, baaaahhhh!?

Memimi: (Are you kidding me... I'm drowning in it,
ughhhhh...! It's too much... I can't drink all of this...!!
This is bad, I'm going to drown in piss... bleeeehhhh...!!)

Thug: She passed out... hahaha, the great Shark Duchess is
napping after drinking my piss!! Should I take a
commemorative photo...

Thug: I got it on video, so let's show everyone!! Once they
see this, the way they look at us will change for sure...
Uploading it to the net sounds good too... or maybe print it
out and scatter it all over town...

Enveloped in a steam of stench that seemed to take form from
ammonia itself, Memimi lay there watching the backs of the
two men chatting away gleefully as they left. Half-
unconsciously, she swallowed the remaining urine in her
mouth...
